<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CHATROOM - Welcome</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .buttons {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .buttons a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .buttons a:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to CHATROOM</h1>
        <p>Your go-to platform for seamless and fun conversations. Connect, share, and chat with friends and family like never before!</p>
        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
            <a href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>Stay connected, stay social. CHATROOM is here for you!</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>